and it kind of makes sense if you think of it, because the technology is still so new.

79
00:03:32,476 --> 00:03:34,538
So anyway, I got these two surveys.

80
00:03:35,279 --> 00:03:39,943
uVisit reported that 14% of 65% wants to try VR,

81
