00:20:50,359 --> 00:20:52,582
up. And the most popular game for that group

386
00:20:53,678 --> 00:20:58,200
was the Brookhaven experiment. So a really tense zombie shooter game.

387
00:20:58,681 --> 00:21:03,023
Now, I do admit in the tests that we did, we didn't have any female players come in.

388
00:21:03,063 --> 00:21:07,585
Sometimes we have them, sometimes we don't. So this might be a little bit gender biased,

389
00:21:07,745 --> 00:21:11,746
but the older adults that we tested these games with wanted something more action oriented

390
00:21:11,766 --> 00:21:12,847
and Brookhaven was a hit.

391
00:21:14,680 --> 00:21:17,682
They liked that it felt like an actual game.

392
00:21:17,863 --> 00:21:19,404
And that's a comment I've heard a couple of times,

393
00:21:19,464 --> 00:21:21,345
while a lot of the VR things didn't really feel

394
00:21:21,365 --> 00:21:22,085
as much as a game.

395
00:21:22,706 --> 00:21:24,327
And they like to shoot and kill things.

396
00:21:25,127 --> 00:21:27,469
Whether it was the archery game that you'll find in the

397
00:21:27,509 --> 00:21:29,170
lab, the slingshot that you'll find in the lab, or

398
00:21:29,971 --> 00:21:33,513
space pirate trainer, this is a mechanic that works for an

399
00:21:34,174 --> 00:21:35,114
older gamer audience.

400
00:21:35,655 --> 00:21:37,856
Now, obviously, I tried some other games as well.

401
00:21:39,426 --> 00:21:41,668
But I was really disappointed with how it turned out.

