00:21:51,037 --> 00:21:55,482
but they didn't really want to keep playing it like they did with the shooting games,

405
00:21:55,682 --> 00:21:59,966
and they felt in particular that the art style was too weird and too childish.

406
00:22:00,787 --> 00:22:06,553
A more lifelike art style, like what you'll see in Valve's lab, works fine,

407
00:22:06,693 --> 00:22:11,438
but when you go into the really cartoony stuff, it's kind of off-putting for 60-plus-year-olds, I guess.

